Name: UFOBIA
About the game: UFOBIA is a first-person action horror adventure where police officers are called in to investigate an ongoing kidnapping in a abandoned mine. Features Survive in the fight against beings from another planet. Explore the woods, villages and an abandoned mine for clues. Solve puzzles and find specific items to advance the investigation. Everything is better with friends! Invite your friends to help with the investigation.
